<div style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 8px; color: #3E2723;">
  <h1 style="color: #5D4037; font-size: 20px; margin: 0 0 20px;">Videira Clinic</h1>

  <p style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6;">Bem-vindo(a)!</p>

  <p style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6;">
    Confirme o e-mail da sua conta (<strong><%= @email %></strong>) clicando no botão abaixo:
  </p>

  <p style="text-align: center; margin: 28px 0;">
    <a href="<%= confirmation_url(@resource, confirmation_token: @token) %>"
       style="background-color: #5D4037; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none;
              padding: 13px 30px; border-radius: 9999px; font-size: 15px; display: inline-block;">
      Confirmar minha conta
    </a>
  </p>

  <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #E0E0E0; margin: 24px 0;">

  <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #8D6E63; margin: 0;">Videira Clinic</p>
</div>
